{
  "texts": [
    "Explainable AI (XAI) is a research area that focuses on revealing the features and patterns used to make decisions, aiming to build trust in AI models.",
    "Kumar and Boulanger (2020) emphasize the significance of explainable AES models for pedagogy.",
    "Exploring XAI in general is an intriguing research topic, and its application to AES models would greatly facilitate the uncovering of features utilized in the scoring process.",
    "Creativity in essay writing is a valuable skill for students as it allows them to express their opinions in a unique and engaging manner.",
    "Assessing the engagement of creative writing and incorporating it into the essay score can greatly enhance overall evaluations in classroom settings."
  ]
}